Thank you for using our app. This Privacy Policy describes how we collect, use, and share your personal information when you use our app.

HOW WE COLLECT DATA
We only collect the personal data that is necessary for using our app. We may collect the following types of personal data:

Name and surname
Email address
Phone number
Date of birth
Gender
Location data
IP address
Device type and operating system
Log data
We collect this data when you create an account, use our app, or contact us for support.

HOW WE USE DATA
We use your personal data to provide and improve our app, and to communicate with you. Specifically, we use your data to:

Create and manage your account
Provide customer support
Personalize your experience
Analyze app usage
Advertise and market our app
We will never sell your personal data to third parties.

HOW WE SHARE DATA
We may share your personal data with third-party service providers who help us operate our app, such as hosting providers or payment processors. We only share your data with these third parties to the extent necessary for them to perform their services.

We may also share your personal data if required by law, to protect our rights or property, or in the event of a merger or acquisition.

DATA RETENTION
We will retain your personal data for as long as necessary to provide our app and fulfill the purposes described in this Privacy Policy, unless a longer retention period is required by law.

YOUR RIGHTS
You have the right to access and control your personal data. Specifically, you have the right to:

Access your personal data
Correct your personal data
Delete your personal data
Object to the processing of your personal data
Withdraw your consent to the processing of your personal data
To exercise these rights, please contact us using the information provided below.

CONTACT US
If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at email: jannahadhaninfo@gmail.com
